{"tid":344144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★蘋果 2017Q3 大中華銷售急跌！Tim Cook：香港「陀衰家」！","createTime":"2017-08-02T05:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T18:21:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62df379919e358aba838c995f7eba91496eccdee","tid":344144,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:16:04.000Z","msg":"蘋果今晨公開 2017Q3 業績，銷售額和盈利同比平穩增長，但是唯獨大中華區的銷售仍然比上一年急跌，最近 Tim Cook 在 CNBC 的訪問將大中華區銷售不振責任全推給香港身上。<br />\n<br />\nTim Cook 在 CNBC 的訪問之中，再次針對香港銷售不振振達不滿，直指香港「陀衰」大中華區銷售，在回答有關大中華銷售急跌的問題的時候，Tim Cook 提及蘋果在中國銷售同比上升了 5%，台灣銷售上升了 20%，但卻指因為香港銷售急跌，拖累大中華區整體下跌，但他沒有提供任何有關香港銷售的數字證明他的講法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/08/02/tim-cook-blames-apple-hong-kong-sales-weak/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2Ftim-cook-blames-apple-hong-kong-sales-weak%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml457TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=57f8fed4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/08/02/tim-cook-blames-apple-hong-kong-sales-weak/</a>"},{"pid":"d8548cb0b1469ac3ddb9d8a1df861c6064553f8d","tid":344144,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ad544cbde5792d4be8914ca5b2f1eebd65fd74","tid":344144,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"IFAN BLOCKED U ALREADY"},{"pid":"a8d0e48af6b67af484b0e16b0ac122d3da426923","tid":344144,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:17:27.000Z","msg":"叫班香港ifandog如何面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset